{
  "texts": [
    "The SHAP methodology just increased the transparency of AI models in some aspects.",
    "Research on AI reliability and transparency is still urgently necessary.",
    "Are there also ways to explain AI models by instructing the rules of models?",
    "This still needs to be explored.Even though the SHAP method explained AI models in some aspects, it already supplied some knowledge about AI models to us humans.",
    "Research by Feifei Li [58] certifies that human interaction will improve the performance of AI models, while the latest GPT4 models [19] also certify the necessary human insertion in large AI models."
